    "image_with_text_v2_mnFUNa": {
      "type": "image-with-text-v2",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_fb3tHx": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Founding Story",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "heading_subheading": "",
            "heading_subheading_size": "h5",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "subheading_KF66pH": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "<strong>Built by Practitioners</strong>",
            "subheading_size": "h3",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "text_ajxjJp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Troscriptions was <strong>founded in 2020 by five healthcare practitioners—four of them medical doctors—</strong>with a shared frustration:<br/>Patients were overwhelmed by modern life and help was needed now for:</p><ul><li>Chronic stress</li><li>Poor sleep</li><li>Brain fog</li><li>Pain</li><li>Low energy</li></ul><p>The issue wasn’t effort. </p><p>It wasn’t motivation. </p><p>It was delivery, dosing, and biology being ignored.</p><p><br/>So we built what didn’t exist.<br/><strong>Physician-formulated, precision-dosed buccal troches</strong>—designed for rapid, reliable absorption and consistent effects, without relying on a stressed gut or guesswork dosing.</p>",
            "text_size": "typeset",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "show_hanging_quotes": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        }
      },
